                    "value": "<p data-visibility=\"gm\"><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature touches any part of the door.</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The door flies open with incredible force. The triggering creature must attempt a <span data-pf2-check=\"reflex\" data-pf2-traits=\"damaging-effect,chaotic,hazard,trap,magical\" data-pf2-label=\"Slam DC\" data-pf2-dc=\"22\" data-pf2-show-dc=\"gm\">Reflex</span> save as the door explodes outward into them, which deals [[/r {5d8}[bludgeoning]]]{5d8 bludgeoning damage}.</p>\n<div data-visibility=\"gm\"><hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature takes no damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and is knocked 10 feet toward the window behind them.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and is knocked 20 feet toward the window. The window shatters and the PC falls 5 feet before colliding with the ground, taking an additional [[/r {2d6}[piercing]]]{2d6 piercing damage} from passing through the broken glass.</p>\n</div>"
